台灣乜事都冇，仲點會好意思問人拎疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:55:43.000Z","msg":"我都覺得誇張左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣疫情唔嚴重<br />\n但美國爆到七彩<br />\n點都係幫自己先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3223250ae5330a769b879d0cb5015c3a594681d","tid":2150321,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:22:55.000Z","msg":"聯合報<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e8b19db1eaf59292d463154e053a7b8148ee9f6","tid":2150321,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73336fe5673341591c70c9f9efb23a94bd704125","tid":2150321,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:50:05.000Z","msg":"台灣洗咩驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"冇可能一直鎖國"}]}